data.description: Don't miss this Newly Built (2023) and Fully Upgraded Townhome in Belmont, a highly desirable resort style amenity and maintenance free community! As soon as you enter the front door, you'll be impressed by the bright and open floor plan, complete with high ceilings and modern 16” tile flooring. The upgraded kitchen features stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, ample cabinetry, and a breakfast bar. At the back of the spacious living room are sliding glass doors out to your covered and screened lanai! Upstairs you’ll find a large loft and laundry room with easy access to the bedrooms. The spacious master suite boasts a large walk-in closet, an ensuite bathroom with dual sinks, and a walk-in glass enclosed shower. The garage provides ample space for your vehicle and storage needs. A couple huge bonus’s this home offers over the other townhomes is the Titan whole house water filter, and newly installed matching fans! Additionally this home comes move in ready and turnkey furnished. Belmont Townhomes is a resort style gated community that includes a luxury beach entry pool, a Olympic sized lap pool, a multipurpose turf field, a playground, tennis courts, basketball courts, two dog parks, all exterior maintenance, and water all for only $175 a month! You'll love the convenient location, just minutes from shopping, dining, and entertainment. Is this home your perfect match? Schedule a showing today!
